Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity

Class ManifestDescription

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.entity.ManifestDescription
public class ManifestDescription extends Object
Describes a manifest, including input/output types and additional parameters.
This class defines the structure of a manifest in the context of workflows or blocks, providing detailed information about the types of inputs, outputs, and various properties such as batch processing capabilities and scalar handling.
